cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
title: Packet‑Rate and Size Dependent Latency and Energy Measurements for L2 Forwarding
abstract: The dataset records packet‑rate and packet‑size sweeps performed with MoonGen
  to generate L2 traffic between two ports while measuring per‑packet latency histograms
  and device‑under‑test energy consumption. A libmoon‑based forwarder script captures
  the same metrics during forwarding, synchronizing start/stop across nodes. Multiple
  runs explore different rate and size configurations, producing raw CSV data and
  plotted PNGs for downstream analysis of latency distributions and power usage. The
  experiment employs a reproducible build environment with huge page support and disabled
  CPU turbo boost to ensure consistent performance.
